descriptionHtml:
İstanbul Sabiha Gökçen International Airport Official Mobile Application for Android.

You can track your flight and receive push notifications. You can also see flights on map.
In destinations screen you can learn where you can fly from/to Sabiha Gökçen and which airline you can fly with.

You can also explore restaurant and cafes, terminal map and car park fees and much more.
